+    `Adjusted interaction coefficient for high_crp_q75 x stage_iv was ${fmt(crpStageInt.estimate)} months (SE ${fmt(crpStageInt.se)}, p=${formatP(crpStageInt.pValue)}).`,
+    "OLS: pfs_months ~ high_crp_q75 * stage_iv + baseline covariates",
+    "refined"
+  );
