The adjusted exploration shows the dataset is dominated by prognostic effects, with regorafenib as the only strong treatment-associated signal and little evidence for targeted treatment-biomarker interactions. I’m adding a broader interaction scan among prognostic and treatment factors to choose the final later iterations.
